How to use:

1. installation of node.js from their website

2. grunt-cli installation
> sudo npm install -g grunt-cli

3. bower installation
> sudo npm install -g bower

4. installing all dependencies of the application, so from the root dir of the app execute the following command
> npm install
> bower install

5. run the application in development mode
> grunt serve

6. or run the application in production mode (code minification)
> grunt serve:dist